snippet.title: Garlic Builder Announcement Trailer| Pixel+Garlic +Building
snippet.description:
The store page of our new game #GarlicBuider is now open! 

 In the game, you will be the protagonist "Garlic", accepting customer orders, following (or not following?) drawings, and using various tools and cubes to complete the craft!
